room_title: Escape room "The Lost Continent" by Epic Escape Game in Denver
room_description: Your Aunt Jaclyn has always been the oddball of the family. An eccentric archaeologist, she often disappears for days at a time. But now there’s been no sign of her for four months, and you’ve been sent to her mansion to search her study for any clues of where she might be. Jaclyn’s other heirs are keen to begin auctioning off her artifacts - you only have one hour to investigate her disappearance and discover the secrets of The Lost Continent.
